metadata.name: ETHereal Journey Tarot Cardback
metadata.description:
The tarot realm is rich with symbolism, and the compass holds a special significance as a guiding tool on the journey of self-discovery and spiritual growth.

It guides us towards our true north path, reminding us to stay centered and connected to our inner compass. 

The ETHereal Journey Tarot card back design represents the compass, our intuition and rationality, urging us to trust our instincts and tap into universal wisdom.
